title: Werewolf In The Amazon, A 2005 Daiana Amêndola, Karina Bacchi, Tania Boscoli, Joana Medeiros, Paul Naschy, Danielle Winitis

sources.title: Werewolf In The Amazon, A 2005 Daiana Amêndola, Karina Bacchi, Tania Boscoli, Joana Medeiros, Paul Naschy, Danielle Winitis
sources.description: Towards the end of his acting career Paul Naschy managed to find lots of roles that put him in close proximity to naked women. This film is no exception to that rule. Some odd mix of The Island of Dr Moreau and a werewolf movie and a bunch of teenagers traveling to the Amazon in search of drugs.
